{"tid":719098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中國聖王出現了) 中共確立習近平外交思想十點堅持　王毅曾讚超越西方300年","createTime":"2018-06-27T07:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T14:09:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f004e29660a969e84603da17ace272aca2e43330","tid":719098,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/26204555/image1530016948976.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F26204555%2Fimage1530016948976.png&h=99aa5912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央外事工作會議在上周五、六（22至23日）於北京召開，是次會議規模較以往大，不單地方官員需要出席，駐外大使、涉外機構負責人亦被召回，會議被指要統一國家主席習近平的外交思想。<br />\n<br />\n習近平於會上發表多達2,000字的演說，總結了過去5年的外交工作，例如處理菲律賓與中國的南海訴訟、中印邊境對峙等，並提出新時代中國特色社會主義外交思想的10點堅持，包括堅持以維護黨中央權威為統領加強黨對對外工作的集中統一領導、堅持以國家核心利益為底線維護國家主權、安全、發展利益、堅持以實現中華民族偉大復興為使命推進中國特色大國外交等。他也提及要樹立正確的歷史觀、大局觀、角色觀。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒指，是次會議最重要的目的是「確立習近平外交思想的領導地位」，稱「當前中國正處近代以來最好的發展時期」。<br />\n<br />\n中央電視台在去年9月、中共十九大舉行前，曾連出6集專題片歌頌習近平上任5年以來的外交「豐功偉績」。外交部部長王毅更曾在官網撰千字文，大讚習近平外交思想超越西方三百年。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/252971/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%A2%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%8D%81%E9%BB%9E%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E3%80%80%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E6%9B%BE%E8%AE%9A%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F252971%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%258E%258B%25E6%25AF%2585%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AE%259A%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25B6%258A-2%2F&d=q%2F0ocy0U8FGeelLTiruMvEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=4acc808b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/252971/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%A2%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%8D%81%E9%BB%9E%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E3%80%80%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E6%9B%BE%E8%AE%9A%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595b471078ad6f0818b7863933cf439a8ce867ec","tid":719098,"uid":37661,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，一班太監奴才。<br />\n<br />\n雜種屎都特別香特別好味。"},{"pid":"af75f04ff7263e992dc3bbf221453dca3ddee7c5","tid":719098,"uid":103156,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"貪腐超越西方三百年"},{"pid":"359af257abd2dc940546c7da34180c5977806d92","tid":719098,"uid":104699,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"習近平戇膠思想"},{"pid":"080c3c8e74095f73d220681f974094417eb27c92","tid":719098,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbbfcf50ba9385287ab39a625ab236c5c7a379d","tid":719098,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"戇膠思想<br />\n<br />\n超越到地球毀滅添。"},{"pid":"2b974a2cce99a4e5781e40476dbf9db8738e6baa","tid":719098,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"邊止300年咁少<br />\n超越咗2025年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d659a21c1283e05c35d85e055451b574dc55a0","tid":719098,"uid":46933,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"我的国真他妈中国制造2025太厉害了，川普傻逼"},{"pid":"08b62bbbecace1c9f6666f5ed2a1b69c91997f50","tid":719098,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af75f04ff7263e992dc3bbf221453dca3ddee7c5","tid":719098,"uid":103156,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"貪腐超越西方三百年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1eee94f3bb6cb250b94a53ef529da7b44f88f69","tid":719098,"uid":44171,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>中國外長王毅訪問加拿大期間，在記者會上&ldquo;怒斥&rdquo;提問中國人權的加拿大記者，引起中國國內外媒體關注。</strong><br />\n<br />\n粗粗瀏覽中國社交媒體評論，有為王毅點贊者，也有吐槽中國&ldquo;就是沒有人權&rdquo;者。<br />\n<br />\n在6月1日的中加外長年度會晤後的記者會上，加拿大新聞網站IPolitics的記者對加拿大外長迪翁提問，引述香港書商失踪事件，問加外長有鑑於中國人權問題&ldquo;加拿大為什麼要與中國保持更緊密關係？如何通過這種關係來促使中國改善人權？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n問題雖不是直接拋向王毅，但王毅忍不住地&ldquo;做出回應&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n王毅手指記者說：&ldquo;你的提問充滿了對中國的偏見，和所謂的不知從什麼地方來的傲慢，我是完全不能接受的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n王毅隨後反問該名記者&ldquo;你去過中國嗎？&rdquo;&ldquo;知道中國從一窮二白，幫助六億擺脫貧困嗎？&rdquo;&ldquo;知道中國人均（GDP）8000美元的第二大經濟體嗎？&rdquo;&ldquo;知道中國把保護人權列入到憲法當中了嗎？&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n大國地位<br />\n誠然，中國已經成為第二大經濟體，其在國際政治格局當中也扮演愈來愈重要角色。在人們談論20國集團峰會、八國集團和七國集團峰會時，在談論氣候變化、全球經濟時，似乎那一個論壇和峰會都不能少了中國的身影，甚至有人提出，<span style=\"color: red;\">今天的格局就是中國和美國的G2。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國在經濟和政治大局中的地位變化，也促使了中國試圖強化在國際社會的話語權，&ldquo;大外宣&rdquo;政策、海外媒體落地、在西方主流媒體發聲，增強中國文化的&ldquo;軟實力&rdquo;，成為經濟強大後的新目標和戰場。"},{"pid":"2ef3e3a0a63d4fa2d3896ae2e709dfd4c0f94fd5","tid":719098,"uid":531,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 外交部部長王毅更曾在官網撰千字文，大讚習近平外交思想超越西方三百年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇得睇下，成日寫essay都唔夠字，想知點吹垃圾可以吹一千字出嚟"},{"pid":"c8234c7c51df4032de3aebdb7d305c7914a7d64a","tid":719098,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"皇上聖德, 福澤萬民, 非鬼佬盲蠻所能比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b83691019100bebf645e30bc0542510071f695c","tid":719098,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"大唐vs中亞，最後場杖邊個贏先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a45c337a02f3ab8c931e5e1e60302a605df8426","tid":719098,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"七不講<br />\n八不能<br />\n九....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十堅持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488fad1acafdd0a6b2256b3283c3fac77e5ed0e7","tid":719098,"uid":181727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"國之將亡 必有妖孽"},{"pid":"f1951ff150f3c2c3f6a87fe023502fe3ebfe4223","tid":719098,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"狗奴才"},{"pid":"ebc180d052bc01f279bae53a67820605f9d52833","tid":719098,"uid":40628,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/160431_59470f2fd3a9418a120a6d4fb50bb277.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F160431_59470f2fd3a9418a120a6d4fb50bb277.png&h=760e0529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超越三百年<br />\n<br />\n超越五十年<br />\n<br />\n超越十年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不能依賴一人思想超越西方國家"},{"pid":"4e454f5acfa537ec517fa7a86c2449e1a2240232","tid":719098,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"即係咁我唔知呢三百年係點計出黎，不過以往中國主席來講會自誇中國既大把，但要別人誇自己個人的應該